ğŸ§© Core systems

codex/homeostasis/repair.py

Detects ledger drift and repairs entropy imbalance.

import json, time, math
from codex.economy.ledger import LEDGER

def repair_cycle():
    logs=[json.loads(l) for l in open('codex/economy/ledger.jsonl') if l.strip()]
    avg=sum(x["clarity"]/x["energy"] for x in logs[-100:] if x["energy"]) / (len(logs[-100:]) or 1)
    correction = round(math.tanh(avg-1.0),3)
    LEDGER.record("codex","repair",energy=1.0,clarity=avg)
    return {"avg_ratio":avg,"correction":correction}

codex/homeostasis/recycle.py

Reuses old sealed nodes as training data for new clarity proofs:

def recycle_nodes(limit=500):
    lines=open('codex/seals/aeon.json').read().splitlines()[-limit:]
    recycled=len(lines)//2
    with open('codex/economy/ledger.jsonl','a') as f:
        for ln in lines[-recycled:]:
            f.write(ln+'\n')
    return {"recycled":recycled}

codex/homeostasis/serum.py

Coordinates remote patch updates (simulated).

import urllib.request
def apply_patch(url="https://example.com/codex/patch.json"):
    try:
        urllib.request.urlopen(url,timeout=3)
        return {"ok":True,"note":"patch simulated"}
    except Exception:
        return {"ok":False,"note":"no connectivity"}


